    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, providing a reliable driving experience for its next owner. While the interior is clean and the exterior paint retains a nice shine, there are a few minor surface scratches and typical interior wear consistent with careful use. All major systems, including the air conditioning and electronics, are fully functional, making this a solid choice for anyone seeking a dependable and presentable car.",
